  "id": "guide/entity/interfaces",
  "title": "Entity Interfaces",
  "contents": "\n\n\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/projects/ngrx.io/content/guide/entity/interfaces.md?message=docs%3A%20describe%20your%20change...\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  </div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n<h1 id=\"entity-interfaces\">Entity Interfaces<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/entity/interfaces#entity-interfaces\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"entitystatet\">EntityState&#x3C;T><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/entity/interfaces#entitystatet\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p>The Entity State is a predefined generic interface for a given entity collection with the following interface:</p>\n<code-example header=\"EntityState Interface\">\ninterface <a href=\"api/entity/EntityState\" class=\"code-anchor\">EntityState</a>&#x3C;V> {\n  <a href=\"api/entity/EntityState#ids\" class=\"code-anchor\">ids</a>: string[] | number[];\n  entities: { [<a href=\"api/data/UpdateResponseData#id\" class=\"code-anchor\">id</a>: string | <a href=\"api/data/UpdateResponseData#id\" class=\"code-anchor\">id</a>: number]: V };\n}\n</code-example>\n<ul>\n<li><code><a href=\"api/entity/EntityState#ids\" class=\"code-anchor\">ids</a></code>: An array of all the primary ids in the collection</li>\n<li><code>entities</code>: A dictionary of entities in the collection indexed by the primary id</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Extend this interface to provide any additional properties for the entity state.</p>\n<p>Usage:</p>\n<code-example header=\"user.reducer.ts\">\n<a href=\"api/store-devtools/DevToolsFeatureOptions#export\" class=\"code-anchor\">export</a> interface User {\n  <a href=\"api/data/UpdateResponseData#id\" class=\"code-anchor\">id</a>: string;\n  name: string;\n}\n\n<a href=\"api/store-devtools/DevToolsFeatureOptions#export\" class=\"code-anchor\">export</a> interface <a href=\"api/store/State\" class=\"code-anchor\">State</a> extends <a href=\"api/entity/EntityState\" class=\"code-anchor\">EntityState</a>&#x3C;User> {\n  // additional entity <a href=\"api/store-devtools/StoreDevtools#state\" class=\"code-anchor\">state</a> properties\n  selectedUserId: string | null;\n}\n</code-example>\n<h2 id=\"entityadaptert\">EntityAdapter&#x3C;T><a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/entity/interfaces#entityadaptert\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p>Provides a generic type interface for the provided entity adapter. The entity adapter provides many collection methods for managing the entity state.</p>\n<p>Usage:</p>\n<code-example header=\"user.reducer.ts\">\n<a href=\"api/store-devtools/DevToolsFeatureOptions#export\" class=\"code-anchor\">export</a> const <a href=\"api/data/EntityCollectionReducerMethods#adapter\" class=\"code-anchor\">adapter</a>: <a href=\"api/entity/EntityAdapter\" class=\"code-anchor\">EntityAdapter</a>&#x3C;User> = <a href=\"api/entity/createEntityAdapter\" class=\"code-anchor\">createEntityAdapter</a>&#x3C;User>();\n</code-example>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/data/EntityCollectionReducerMethods#adapter\n - api/data/UpdateResponseData#id\n - api/entity/EntityAdapter\n - api/entity/EntityState\n - api/entity/EntityState#ids\n - api/entity/createEntityAdapter\n - api/store-devtools/DevToolsFeatureOptions#export\n - api/store-devtools/StoreDevtools#state\n - api/store/State\n - guide/entity/interfaces#entity-interfaces\n - guide/entity/interfaces#entityadaptert\n - guide/entity/interfaces#entitystatet\n - https://github.com/ngrx/platform/edit/master/projects/ngrx.io/content/guide/entity/interfaces.md?message=docs%3A%20describe%20your%20change...\n-->"
}